for loop
The For-Loop is comfortable for iterating. It takes three arguments.
â€¢ Initialization (i=0;)
â€¢ Condition (i < 5;)
â€¢ Iteration statement (i+=1)


â€¢ Consider a program printing the numbers 1 to 10:
